# PvtPpr-Generator URI
Pass inputs through nodejs to generate a paper type result for the user to publish their thoughts without needing more than their browser. This generator can also run off itty.bitty.site technology. This is the hash based URI of the current PvtPpr Generator which is not compressed but is still encoded in Base64 to be opened as a webpage in the web-browser. This is considered a "Unsecure" way to visit the PvtPpr Generator by many browsers for it is a URI with a Hash which could include anything which cannot be seen/determined from the face hash.


The feature this version hashlink or hash based URI presents is the hash based URI was built off an ittybitty hashlink generator.
